{% layout 'theme' %}

<section class="page container">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <div class="rte">
    <p><em>Last updated: {{ 'now' | date: '%B %Y' }}</em></p>

    <p>GrayMuzzle Co. is a brand of <strong>Revvy LLC</strong> ("we", "us"). This policy explains what personal information we collect, how we use it, and your rights.</p>

    <h2>1. What we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Order information:</strong> name, shipping address, billing address, email, phone, payment info (processed and stored by Shopify/Stripe, not by us).</li>
      <li><strong>Account information (optional):</strong> email + password if you choose to create an account.</li>
      <li><strong>Communications:</strong> emails and chats you send us.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> pages viewed, device/browser type, IP address, referrer — via cookies and similar technologies (Shopify analytics, Meta Pixel, TikTok Pixel, Klaviyo).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How we use it</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Fulfill orders and provide customer service</li>
      <li>Send transactional emails (order confirmation, shipping updates)</li>
      <li>Send marketing emails (only if you opt in — you can unsubscribe at any time)</li>
      <li>Fight fraud and abuse</li>
      <li>Improve the Site and our product selection</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Who we share with</h2>
    <p>We share personal information with service providers that help us run the business: Shopify (commerce platform), Zendrop and Spocket (fulfillment), Klaviyo (email), Meta and TikTok (advertising), Stripe (payments). We do not sell your personal information.</p>

    <h2>4. Your rights</h2>
    <p>If you live in California (CCPA), the EEA/UK (GDPR), or another jurisdiction with privacy rights, you can ask us to access, correct, or delete your personal information, or to stop processing it for marketing. Email <a href="mailto:privacy@graymuzzle.co">privacy@graymuzzle.co</a> and we will respond within 30 days.</p>
    <p><strong>Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information (California):</strong> We do not sell personal information for money. We do use advertising cookies that may count as "sharing" under the CCPA — you can opt out by emailing the address above or by using the Global Privacy Control signal in your browser.</p>

    <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use essential cookies (to keep your cart working), analytics cookies (to understand traffic), and advertising cookies (to show you relevant ads on Meta and TikTok). You can disable non-essential cookies in your browser or via our cookie banner.</p>

    <h2>6. Retention</h2>
    <p>We keep order records for seven years for tax and legal reasons. Marketing data is deleted within 90 days of your unsubscribe.</p>

    <h2>7. Security</h2>
    <p>Payment data is processed over TLS and never touches our servers — it is handled by Shopify/Stripe, both PCI-DSS certified. We use role-based access and multi-factor authentication for admin accounts.</p>

    <h2>8. Children</h2>
    <p>Our Site is not intended for children under 16 and we do not knowingly collect data from them.</p>

    <h2>9. Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy; the "Last updated" date will change. Material changes will be announced by email or on the Site.</p>

    <h2>10. Contact</h2>
    <p>Revvy LLC, d/b/a GrayMuzzle Co. &middot; <a href="mailto:privacy@graymuzzle.co">privacy@graymuzzle.co</a></p>
  </div>
</section>
